OL,3,  MINISTRY OF SUSTAINABILITY      Q "###
OL,5,C Goulash Gary has announced the final  
OL,6,C purification of the RSG9 tunnel       
OL,7,C complex, ten years after the "Minor   
OL,8,C Ventilation Incident".                
OL,10,F Under the guidance of THE LEADER, the 
OL,11,FFdeep-level site will now serve the    
OL,12,F people. The Great Hero has graciously 
OL,13,F designated the primary dry vaults for 
OL,14,F the storage of Goujon John's private  
OL,15,F wine and kefir collection.            
OL,17,  "His vintage reflects His wisdom,"    
OL,18,F says Grigory Volkoff,G"and the kefir  
OL,19,  will remain perfectly chilled."       
